# Product Definition — {{CERT_NAME}} Lab Series

## Initial Concept
A comprehensive set of hands-on labs for the {{CERT_NAME}} ({{EXAM_CODE}}) exam.

## Target Audience
- **{{CERT_NAME}} ({{EXAM_CODE}}) Exam Candidates:** Individuals seeking structured, hands-on practice to master exam blueprint topics.
- **Experienced Network Engineers:** Professionals looking to refresh core knowledge through practical lab work.

## Core Goals
- **GNS3 Apple Silicon Optimization:** Ensure all topologies and device platforms (c3725, c7200) are fully compatible and performant on Apple M1/M2/M3 hardware.
- **DeepSeek Standard Workbooks:** Deliver standardized, high-quality lab guides that include detailed objectives, step-by-step configuration, verification procedures, and full solutions.

## Key Features
- **Verification Cheatsheets:** Concise cheat sheets for every lab.
- **Standardized Topology Diagrams:** Cisco-compliant network diagrams in editable (Draw.io) and visual (PNG) formats.
- **Troubleshooting Scenarios:** Exam-style fault scenarios with automated injection scripts.
- **Automated Fault Injection:** Python scripts to inject and restore troubleshooting scenarios.
- **Traffic Engineering & Filtering:** Advanced route control using prefix-lists, distribute-lists, and route-maps.

